'''Kitasu Hill''' is a young [[basalt]]ic [[cinder cone]] on southwestern [[Swindle Island]] on the coast of the [[Provinces and territories of Canada|Canadian province]] of [[British Columbia]]. It is located {{Unit km|17|0}} southwest of [[Klemtu, British Columbia|Klemtu]] and south of [[Kitasu Bay]]. Kitasu Hill produced [[lava flow]]s that extend to the north. It is the most prominent volcano of the [[Milbanke Sound Group]].

